item.title: Discussion Questions
item.description: We envision different kinds of analyses that could be done with the WHAMP model related to ADAP and/or PrEP-DAP. We would like your thoughts on the kinds of analyses that would be of greatest interest to you and the kinds of outputs / projections that would be most useful in informing your work. Evaluating impact of program changes 1. What are the kinds of ADAP and/or PrEP-DAP changes/scenarios that you would like to evaluate using the WHAMP model?
